    <p class="paragraph">If you can squeeze it into 280 of your juiciest characters then Twitter is the place to do it! Be warned though, my timeline has no profanity&nbsp;filter.</p>
    <p class="paragraph">
      <a class="btn" href="{{ social.twitter.link }}">{{ social.twitter.username }}</a>
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="contact__social reveal reveal--3">
    <h3 class="heading heading--h3">Social</h3>
    <ul class="paragraph">
      {% for key in ["instagram", "github", "strava", "codepen", "linkedin"] %}
